==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Omni-
<hw>Om"ni-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>omnis</ets> all.]</ety>
<def>A combining form denoting <sig>all</sig>, <sig>every</sig>,
<sig>everywhere</sig>; <as>as in <ex>omni</ex>potent, all-powerful;
<ex>omni</ex>present; <ex>omni</ex>vorous</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Omnibus</ent>⟦br⟧
